Package: pba
Version: 0.2-3
Date: 2011-04-10
Title: Probabilistic Bias Analysis
Author@R: person("Jeremy", "Hetzel", "Thoms", email =
    "jthetzel@gmail.com")
Author: Jeremy T. Hetzel <jthetzel@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Jeremy T. Hetzel <jthetzel@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.12.0), plyr, ggplot2, reshape, fUtilities
Description: The pba package performs probabilistic bias analyses with
    methods adapted from Lash TL, Fox MP, and Fink AK's Applying
    Quantitative Bias Analysis to Epidemiological Data (2010). The
    package can adjust for multiple sources of misclassification,
    selection, and unmeasured confounding bias.
License: GPL-3
URL: http://pba.r-forge.r-project.org/
BugReports:
    https://r-forge.r-project.org/tracker/?func=add&group_id=988&atid=3913
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Collate: 'pba.R'
